name: Kashima (Kantai Collection / Kancolle)
description:
The forgotten succubus is back xD

Read This befroe using my model.

Next is Yamato or Warspite, probably. The exist Kongou model doesn't look good, maybe the another choice.

(Yeh, the easy-to-use LoRA guide has made bad LoRAs spreading anywhere, but yeah, this is Internet, andeveryone need time to learn how to properly use it.)

Contain all official outifts (OG, Rigging OG, Lawson, Valentine, Christmas, Mitsukoshi Casual) + Shimakaze Cosplay + Idonum's black Kashima.

Can wear any other outfit you want & NSFW capable, untested though (Y'now, lack of imagination, and I'm not good at making lewd pics for fapping). You can take Haruna for reference, they are trained with same methods.

Trained on AnimeFull-Final-Pruned.

As you can see, it won't work well on those easy-to-use models.

I want to post a image here for reference, but CivitAI is boom boom again. FFS.

  • Suggest: Anything V3/5, expmix,

  • Meh: MixPro, Dalcefo,

  • Throw-it-to-garbage-bin: Orangemix, Counterfeitv2.5.

Trigger Words:

CAUTION: DO NOT USE Kashima \(Kancolle\) FOR ANY OTHER OUTFITS EXCEPT OG VERSION!!

Most of skirts except shimakaze cosplay and casual one are same, you can choose a bit longer or shorter by using one ofpleated skirt or miniskirt

  • Mitsukoshi Casual：

  • Lawson Collab：
